text: You're welcome to Teban Place with grace. Life is meaningful here. Most of your needs, wants, and wishes come true.

Has many shops and services that serve the local community. This includes two coffeeshops with a good range of food choices, barbers, self-service 24H laundromat, 24H Sheng Siong supermarket, bakeries, hardware stores, clinic, fruits store, furniture store, 7-11, pharmacies, Chinese medical halls, provision stores and ATMs. 61 Teban Place has basically most of the goods and services required for daily necessities by everyone living in the area.
Neighbourhood shopping place with 2 eating house. Nice & cheap food available.
